Invocation Name: harvest olney
des: Listen to the latest messages from Harvest Intercontinental Church, Olney. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to podcasts you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next sermons by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next". This skill was created by Harvest Intercontinental Church Olney's Media Department. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
